item.title: CVE-2020-6278|2024-08-04T08:55:22.330Z -- sap%20se -- sap%20business%20objects%20business%20intelligence%20platform%20%28bi%20launchpad%20and%20cmc%29
item.description: SAP Business Objects Business Intelligence Platform (BI Launchpad and CMC), versions 4.1, 4.2, allows to an attacker to embed malicious scripts in the application while uploading images, which gets executed when the victim opens these files, leading to Stored Cross Site Scripting
